# Netlify redirects
# Place this file (as _redirects, no extension) in the same directory you
# deploy as your site root, so the nav links on the landing page
# (/admin and /client) resolve to the two dashboards.
#
# If you deploy landing/, admin-dashboard/, and client-dashboard/ together
# as one Netlify site (recommended), put this file at the root alongside them.

/admin      /admin-dashboard/index.html    200
/client     /client-dashboard/index.html   200
